title: Hour 2 - Lamar Jackson's Contract, Tom Brady's Family, Rob McElhenney
itunes:title: Hour 2 - Lamar Jackson's Contract, Tom Brady's Family, Rob McElhenney
description:
Dan discusses the Baltimore Ravens and the Lamar Jackson contract situation. Plus, Tom Brady's continued pull between football and family and how it could impact his season. Rob McElhenney stops by to discuss purchasing a soccer club on the new FX docu-series "Welcome to Wrexham."

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
